  "instructions": [
    "Heat a wok or heavy‑bottomed skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add 1 tbsp olive oil and fry the tofu cubes until golden on all sides; remove and set aside.",
    "In the same pan, add the remaining 1 tbsp oil and sauté cumin, coriander, paprika, and ginger until fragrant, about 30 seconds.",
    "Stir in the tomato paste and cook for 1 minute to caramelize.",
    "Pour in water, lemon juice, orange blossom water, and a pinch of salt; bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Return the tofu to the pan, cover, and cook for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally, until the sauce thickens and the tofu soaks the flavors.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning if needed.",
    "Transfer to a serving dish, sprinkle with chopped cilantro.",
    "Optionally, garnish with toasted slivered almonds if desired."
  ],
